{
  "stem": "16792.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Also when I was even a little bit over 13 years old, I walked two, tree hours a day, and hour a day, you know, And this is the way it was.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When I was already 15 years old, I-- my father talked to somebody to give me a job, and he find for me a job in a different city, Sosnoweic, Poland And the job was, because I am a religious person, done with-- with room and board.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the store, the name of the company, was Scoczilas, in Sosnoweic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Scoczilas.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "S-C-O-C-Z-I-L-A-S, Scoczilas.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he has got not the big store.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He has got a medium store, or small or medium store, supplies for-- for manufacturers of suits and dresses, all supplies.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was working down there, and I don't need any money because I was going with him to the-- to the-- to the Shul all the time, and you know.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then all the money which I make, I sent it home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This is the way it was in our family, or in every family, I think, in Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Most religious family did that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I build up the store, and I was going out to small manufacturers, medium manufacturers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I put in new customers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was a kid, 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were so busy that he must take a bigger store.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when he took a bigger store, I told him I would like to-- and I was already a buyer in this particular time, and I was sending to Bedzin.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's not far from Sosnowiec, this city, Bedzin, which we have big wholesalers from this particular part.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And after that, he send me when I was already 16 years old, he send me two Lodz.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
